} resource_access keys must include a colon. PgDoorman ignores everything before it and matches the suffix against general.talos.databases. A token built without the colon prefix will produce no role and authentication will fail with "Token may not contain valid roles for the requested databases". A client connecting to inventory with this token lands in the read_write user (max of the two listed roles).
